# Cloudflare Pages same-origin proxy.
#
# These rules forward authenticated API surfaces from the landing host to the
# Render-hosted wavervanir-api so the browser sees only one origin (no CORS).
#
# Update the destination host once a custom domain is wired (e.g.
# https://api-staging.wavervanir.com). The format is documented at
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/.

/v1/*       https://wavervanir-api.onrender.com/v1/:splat      200
/onboard    https://wavervanir-api.onrender.com/onboard        200
/stripe/*   https://wavervanir-api.onrender.com/stripe/:splat  200
/health     https://wavervanir-api.onrender.com/health         200
